\"right\">3.35%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>運動施設 (Sports Complexes) — 1,912 Visitors (0.47% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table>\n<tr><th>Name</th><th align=\"right\">Annual Visitors</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th><th align=\"right\">% of 運動施設 Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td>新青森県総合運動公園</td><td align=\"right\">687,603</td><td align=\"right\">1,319</td><td align=\"right\">68.99%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>弘前市運動公園</td><td align=\"right\">169,912</td><td align=\"right\">326</td><td align=\"right\">17.05%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>岩木山総合公園</td><td align=\"right\">60,257</td><td align=\"right\">116</td><td align=\"right\">6.07%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>河西体育センター</td><td align=\"right\">41,140</td><td align=\"right\">79</td><td align=\"right\">4.13%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>弘前市立岩木Ｂ＆Ｇ海洋センター</td><td align=\"right\">37,470</td><td align=\"right\">72</td><td align=\"right\">3.77%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>神社 (Shrines) — 1,383 Visitors (0.34% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table>\n<tr><th>Name</th><th align=\"right\">Annual Visitors</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th><th align=\"right\">% of 神社 Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td>高山稲荷神社</td><td align=\"right\">422,300</td><td align=\"right\">926</td><td align=\"right\">66.96%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>岩木山神社</td><td align=\"right\">105,000</td><td align=\"right\">230</td><td align=\"right\">16.63%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>猿賀神社</td><td align=\"right\">103,500</td><td align=\"right\">227</td><td align=\"right\">16.41%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>スキー場 (Ski Resorts) — 93 Visitors (0.02% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table>\n<tr><th>Name</th><th align=\"right\">Annual Visitors</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th><th align=\"right\">% of スキー場 Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td>モヤヒルズ（スキー場）</td><td align=\"right\">55,749</td><td align=\"right\">53</td><td align=\"right\">56.99%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>ロマントピアスキー場</td><td align=\"right\">12,814</td><td align=\"right\">20</td><td align=\"right\">21.51%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>大鰐温泉スキー場</td><td align=\"right\">16,577</td><td align=\"right\">20</td><td align=\"right\">21.51%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>テーマパーク (Theme Parks) — 1,802 Visitors (0.44% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table>\n<tr><th>Name</th><th align=\"right\">Annual Visitors</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th><th align=\"right\">% of テーマパーク Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td>弘前市立観光館</td><td align=\"right\">394,986</td><td align=\"right\">1,082</td><td align=\"right\">60.04%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>板柳町ふるさとセンター</td><td align=\"right\">172,994</td><td align=\"right\">474</td><td align=\"right\">26.30%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>田んぼアート（田舎館村展望台）</td><td align=\"right\">78,561</td><td align=\"right\">215</td><td align=\"right\">11.93%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>ストーブ列車（津軽鉄道）</td><td align=\"right\">11,378</td><td align=\"right\">31</td><td align=\"right\">1.72%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n## Methodology\n\nResident and commuter totals are derived from employed persons (就業者数) and workers (従業者数) per small census area (小地域), refined by 500m labor mesh and 250m/100m resident mesh to achieve sub-district point placement. Population counts are conserved at the 小地域 level, and point placement is optimized via a mesh-aware loss function.\n\nCommute patterns are modeled using a gravity model augmented by known origin-destination flows at the municipality (市町村) or designated city ward (区) level.\n\n## Data Sources\n\n- 令和2年国勢調査 (2020 National Census) — [e-Stat](https://www.e-stat.go.jp/)\n- 令和3年経済センサス (2021 Economic Census) — [e-Stat](https://www.e-stat.go.jp/)\n- 簡易100mメッシュ人口 (100m Mesh Population) — [GTFS-GIS](https://gtfs-gis.jp/teikyo/)\n- 国土数値情報 (National Land Numerical Information) — [MLIT](https://nlftp.mlit.go.jp/)\n- 空港管理状況調査 (Airport Management Statistics) — [MLIT Aviation](https://www.mlit.go.jp/koku/15_bf_000185.html)\n- 港湾調査 (Port Survey) — [MLIT Ports](https://www.mlit.go.jp/k-toukei/kouwan.html)\n- 大学ポートレート (University Portraits) — [JASSO](https://portraits.niad.ac.jp/)\n- 学校基本調査 (School Basic Survey) — [MEXT](https://www.mext.go.jp/)\n- 観光統計 (Tourism Statistics) — [JNTO](https://statistics.jnto.go.jp/)\n- Overture Maps Foundation — [Overture](https://overturemaps.org/)\n- 海しる / J-EGG500 (Ocean Information / Bathymetry) — [MSIL](https://www.msil.go.jp/) / [JODC](https://www.jodc.go.jp/)\n\n## License\n\nThis map data is released under the [MIT License](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT).\n\n## Attribution\n\nData derived from the following government and public data sources. See **Data Sources** above for links.\n\n- **Population & Commuting**: 令和2年国勢調査 (2020 National Census), 令和3年経済センサス (2021 Economic Census)\n- **Geospatial**: 国土数値情報 (National Land Numerical Information), Overture Maps Foundation\n- **Institutions**: 学校基本調査, 大学ポートレート, 空港管理状況調査, 港湾調査\n- **Tourism**: 観光統計 (Tourism Statistics)\n- **Bathymetry**: 海しる / J-EGG500",
